text: WSVQ-LP (92.1 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Charleston West Side, West Virginia. The station is owned by the Partnership of African American Churches. It airs a variety radio format. The station was assigned the WSVQ-LP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on April 3, 2015. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * SVQ-LP SVQ-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2017 Category:2017 establishments in the United States Category:Variety radio stations in the United States Category:Kanawha County, West Virginia
